metadata.name: Skully
metadata.description:
Handcrafted one of one characters by Steven Daily.

I manifested my original "Imposter" drawing in 1999.  He was born from the “imposter syndrome” I felt from being out of my element as a graffiti writer transitioning from the streets to the gallery.  Painting this character on walls and freight trains around Southern California helped me process this new chapter in my artistic journey.
